1
00:00:14,656 --> 00:00:18,240
♪Long and short,
sighs are whispers sharp as blades♪

2
00:00:18,976 --> 00:00:23,026
♪East and west, hustling and drifting
in the martial world♪

3
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,816
♪Destined or accidental,
no one falls for me♪

4
00:00:27,759 --> 00:00:31,232
♪Solitary is my middle name♪

5
00:00:32,064 --> 00:00:35,680
♪Spring after spring,
is the matchmaker dozing off♪

6
00:00:36,288 --> 00:00:39,872
♪You knock on the door of my heart,
a burst of blossoms amazing the dusk♪

7
00:00:40,576 --> 00:00:44,192
♪Touching or hurting,
we tacitly agree it's a kind of fortune♪

8
00:00:44,416 --> 00:00:48,867
♪The blue and the rosy
are heaven's match♪

9
00:00:49,504 --> 00:00:54,432
♪Falling into an embrace,
cherishing a moment of tenderness♪

10
00:00:54,624 --> 00:00:58,624
♪No need to mind at all
the blush on the cheeks♪

11
00:00:58,848 --> 00:01:02,944
♪Amid laughter and talk,
longing becomes words on the paper♪

12
00:01:03,488 --> 00:01:06,464
♪From now on, the delicate thoughts
speak no separation♪

13
00:01:06,464 --> 00:01:10,528
♪In the song that warms the world,
I only care for one person♪

14
00:01:10,528 --> 00:01:15,168
♪Before the autumn rain pours,
you hold the umbrella, and I wait♪

15
00:01:15,168 --> 00:01:19,264
♪Being deeply moved,
this life bears no regrets♪

16
00:01:19,264 --> 00:01:21,760
♪Flowers swaying,
we listen deep into the night♪

17
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:25,381
♪I wish the prime of youth favor you,
witnessed by the sun and moon♪

18
00:01:25,907 --> 00:01:31,497
=To Get Master=
(Based on The Fierce Princess by Jun Su)

19
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,960
=Episode 19=

20
00:01:37,659 --> 00:01:38,659
Leave?

21
00:01:39,418 --> 00:01:40,579
What?

22
00:01:40,978 --> 00:01:42,379
I want to retire.

23
00:01:43,099 --> 00:01:44,778
Let's live a peaceful life then.

24
00:01:46,898 --> 00:01:48,299
Retire?

25
00:01:49,659 --> 00:01:50,778
Are you saying

26
00:01:51,179 --> 00:01:52,379
you won't be the villain

27
00:01:52,539 --> 00:01:53,539
and keep fighting?

28
00:02:01,019 --> 00:02:02,058
Great!

29
00:02:02,978 --> 00:02:04,459
Although I also want to see you

30
00:02:04,579 --> 00:02:06,258
punish those hypocrites,

31
00:02:06,858 --> 00:02:08,418
as the saying goes,

32
00:02:08,978 --> 00:02:10,579
there is never an end of taking revenge.

33
00:02:11,099 --> 00:02:11,848
Moreover,

34
00:02:12,379 --> 00:02:12,939
why would we

35
00:02:12,939 --> 00:02:14,258
waste our time

36
00:02:14,939 --> 00:02:16,584
to fight with those fools?

37
00:02:20,339 --> 00:02:20,968
Before,

38
00:02:22,298 --> 00:02:23,528
I only wanted to seek revenge,

39
00:02:24,219 --> 00:02:25,539
making those who severely hurt me

40
00:02:26,059 --> 00:02:27,560
and my kin to pay their price.

41
00:02:29,138 --> 00:02:30,219
But now,

42
00:02:31,698 --> 00:02:33,320
I found that I have no hatred anymore.

43
00:02:34,619 --> 00:02:35,978
What I think of and yearns for

44
00:02:37,018 --> 00:02:38,018
is only you.

45
00:02:41,659 --> 00:02:42,659
So, Song'er,

46
00:02:43,539 --> 00:02:44,659
you have changed me.

47
00:02:46,298 --> 00:02:47,578
You are important to me.

48
00:02:48,698 --> 00:02:50,698
I really don't want you to

49
00:02:51,178 --> 00:02:52,258
live in fear by my side.

50
00:02:54,258 --> 00:02:55,258
However...

51
00:02:56,659 --> 00:02:57,899
I still worry...

52
00:02:59,258 --> 00:03:00,258
What?

53
00:03:00,738 --> 00:03:02,138
If we retire,

54
00:03:02,899 --> 00:03:04,899
we'll have
to live a normal life like others.

55
00:03:06,059 --> 00:03:08,738
And I can only rely on
physical labor to make a living.

56
00:03:09,819 --> 00:03:10,819
I won't be able

57
00:03:11,138 --> 00:03:13,128
to give you a luxurious life soon.

58
00:03:13,779 --> 00:03:14,568
If you are with me,

59
00:03:15,178 --> 00:03:16,552
you might have to suffer.

60
00:03:22,138 --> 00:03:22,984
I knew it.

61
00:03:23,499 --> 00:03:25,320
You want me
to live a hard life with you.

62
00:03:27,418 --> 00:03:28,360
No way.

63
00:03:29,448 --> 00:03:29,992
Well...

64
00:03:33,339 --> 00:03:34,504
Just kidding.

65
00:03:35,528 --> 00:03:36,776
I can make fragrances.

66
00:03:37,379 --> 00:03:38,280
If you are with me,

67
00:03:38,779 --> 00:03:40,178
you will enjoy good days.

68
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,360
I will open a fragrance shop
and sell spices.

69
00:03:44,819 --> 00:03:45,320
And you'll

70
00:03:45,858 --> 00:03:47,258
use your martial skills

71
00:03:47,458 --> 00:03:48,424
to guard for me.

72
00:03:50,499 --> 00:03:53,059
Therefore, I'll have
to rely on you in the future.

73
00:03:54,899 --> 00:03:55,688
But in a few days,

74
00:03:56,978 --> 00:03:58,978
I think Nan Wentian
will threaten Chu Mengdie

75
00:03:59,418 --> 00:04:01,178
to lead people to the Riyue Palace

76
00:04:01,619 --> 00:04:02,659
for my life.

77
00:04:03,178 --> 00:04:04,619
At the coffin home of Nanshan,

78
00:04:05,099 --> 00:04:06,698
I've prepared a male corpse

79
00:04:06,939 --> 00:04:07,912
with a similar figure

80
00:04:08,539 --> 00:04:09,448
but a blur face.

81
00:04:11,059 --> 00:04:11,720
By then,

82
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:14,418
I will put him
in the underground palace.

83
00:04:16,178 --> 00:04:17,219
In that case,

84
00:04:18,659 --> 00:04:20,328
I can fake my death to escape.

85
00:04:23,339 --> 00:04:24,584
You have prepared everything?

86
00:04:26,259 --> 00:04:27,208
I've already checked.

87
00:04:28,168 --> 00:04:29,384
To the south of Chiqian City,

88
00:04:30,099 --> 00:04:31,400
a small town called Flower City

89
00:04:32,459 --> 00:04:34,248
is isolated from the world,

90
00:04:34,779 --> 00:04:35,880
but filled with nice folks.

91
00:04:37,339 --> 00:04:38,184
All year round,

92
00:04:38,818 --> 00:04:40,680
there blooms with flowers all over.

93
00:04:41,178 --> 00:04:41,896
By then,

94
00:04:42,339 --> 00:04:43,858
we can settle down there

95
00:04:43,978 --> 00:04:44,978
before we set up a plan.

96
00:04:45,738 --> 00:04:46,738
Great.

97
00:04:48,104 --> 00:04:48,776
Flower City.

98
00:04:50,498 --> 00:04:53,288
It sounds very suitable
for me to live in.

99
00:04:56,058 --> 00:04:57,058
By then,

100
00:04:57,339 --> 00:04:59,339
you can start a fragrance shop there.

101
00:05:00,178 --> 00:05:02,099
That will be a new beginning for us.

102
00:05:02,818 --> 00:05:05,416
But my body hasn't recovered yet.

103
00:05:06,099 --> 00:05:08,392
And this must not be known to others.

104
00:05:09,539 --> 00:05:11,899
So, please go to the coffin home
to send a message

105
00:05:12,259 --> 00:05:12,776
for me.

106
00:05:14,298 --> 00:05:14,888
Okay.

107
00:05:29,699 --> 00:05:30,920
This drumstick is mine.

108
00:05:32,498 --> 00:05:33,032
Father.

109
00:05:34,019 --> 00:05:35,019
Is the drumstick tasty?

110
00:05:35,019 --> 00:05:35,720
Yes.

111
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,618
Really?

112
00:05:36,938 --> 00:05:37,579
It's still warm.

113
00:05:37,659 --> 00:05:38,779
Freshly roasted. Eat more.

114
00:05:41,178 --> 00:05:42,178
By the way, Nan.

115
00:05:42,378 --> 00:05:43,498
I took another job.

116
00:05:43,858 --> 00:05:44,616
I'm in a hurry.

117
00:05:45,032 --> 00:05:45,736
So,

118
00:05:45,992 --> 00:05:47,058
I have to go

119
00:05:47,139 --> 00:05:48,139
after finishing it.

120
00:05:48,699 --> 00:05:49,699
Okay.

121
00:05:55,944 --> 00:05:56,840
May I ask

122
00:05:56,968 --> 00:05:59,539
who is "Nan" your father mentioned?

123
00:06:00,579 --> 00:06:01,618
He is a friend

124
00:06:01,899 --> 00:06:03,779
who used to practice martial arts
with him.

125
00:06:05,618 --> 00:06:06,818
But they haven't met for long.

126
00:06:09,858 --> 00:06:10,858
Sir.

127
00:06:11,699 --> 00:06:13,818
What illness my father has?

128
00:06:13,992 --> 00:06:16,219
Just now, I took your father's pulse

129
00:06:16,328 --> 00:06:18,978
and found his pulse to be chaotic
with excessive yang energy.

130
00:06:19,378 --> 00:06:21,139
Normally, this kind of pulse is a sign

131
00:06:21,339 --> 00:06:22,600
of life-threatening danger.

132
00:06:23,298 --> 00:06:24,498
But upon careful examination,

133
00:06:25,139 --> 00:06:27,219
I felt that all his pulses
are all connected,

134
00:06:27,858 --> 00:06:28,938
not endangering his life.

135
00:06:29,298 --> 00:06:30,498
Weird.

136
00:06:31,944 --> 00:06:32,552
Sir.

137
00:06:33,128 --> 00:06:34,339
Any way to treat this?

138
00:06:34,504 --> 00:06:35,144
Miss.

139
00:06:35,539 --> 00:06:37,659
Forgive my limited medical skills.

140
00:06:37,659 --> 00:06:38,858
I'll take my leave.

141
00:06:39,019 --> 00:06:40,779
Thank you. Take care.

142
00:06:58,659 --> 00:07:02,472
Mengdie, what did the physician say?

143
00:07:04,392 --> 00:07:06,536
He said there is no medicine

144
00:07:07,339 --> 00:07:08,552
for his illness.

145
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,899
When he fell ill,

146
00:07:12,498 --> 00:07:14,818
I sought physicians for consultations,

147
00:07:15,418 --> 00:07:17,576
and got the same answers.

148
00:07:18,139 --> 00:07:20,808
I realized that he had gone astray.

149
00:07:21,672 --> 00:07:23,019
I wanted to tell you

150
00:07:23,339 --> 00:07:25,378
that there's no need to find physicians.

151
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,856
But in my opinion,

152
00:07:28,099 --> 00:07:31,272
his condition has worsened recently.

153
00:07:32,219 --> 00:07:34,099
You mean...

154
00:07:35,219 --> 00:07:36,219
In the past,

155
00:07:36,498 --> 00:07:37,498
he

156
00:07:37,699 --> 00:07:39,699
didn't know his name

157
00:07:39,858 --> 00:07:40,858
or where he came from,

158
00:07:41,498 --> 00:07:43,498
but he could still go out
and take on tasks.

159
00:07:45,019 --> 00:07:48,459
Recently, he even struggles
to speak coherently.

160
00:07:48,938 --> 00:07:50,938
Perhaps he's getting old.

161
00:07:51,418 --> 00:07:53,339
Those unresolved concerns

162
00:07:54,659 --> 00:07:56,539
have haunted him

163
00:07:57,139 --> 00:07:58,899
and disturbed his mind.

164
00:08:05,178 --> 00:08:06,339
Mengdie,

165
00:08:07,498 --> 00:08:09,058
don't blame yourself.

166
00:08:09,418 --> 00:08:10,219
If he knew

167
00:08:10,339 --> 00:08:11,738
that you have replaced him

168
00:08:12,019 --> 00:08:13,459
as the leader of martial world,

169
00:08:13,818 --> 00:08:15,459
he will surely be happy for you.

170
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,938
Happy?

171
00:08:21,099 --> 00:08:22,378
If so,

172
00:08:26,019 --> 00:08:27,539
why did he become like this

173
00:08:27,659 --> 00:08:29,459
after being the leader?

174
00:08:30,858 --> 00:08:32,339
He must feel guilt and unwillingness

175
00:08:32,498 --> 00:08:34,339
to the martial world.

176
00:08:34,779 --> 00:08:36,339
I wonder if he could start all over,

177
00:08:38,098 --> 00:08:39,619
what choice would he make?

178
00:08:40,098 --> 00:08:41,379
If he could start over,

179
00:08:41,539 --> 00:08:44,904
he would surely choose this same path.

180
00:08:46,098 --> 00:08:47,539
The martial world is dangerous.

181
00:08:47,698 --> 00:08:51,098
Right and wrong are often
decided in a moment's thought.

182
00:08:51,698 --> 00:08:53,298
Sometimes, for the sake of people,

183
00:08:53,499 --> 00:08:55,098
a choice must be made.

184
00:08:56,058 --> 00:08:59,178
As long as the choice
is made with good intentions,

185
00:08:59,698 --> 00:09:00,698
naturally,

186
00:09:00,779 --> 00:09:02,938
it will lead to a good result.

187
00:09:03,938 --> 00:09:05,619
With good intentions,

188
00:09:06,659 --> 00:09:07,979
one will reap a good result.

189
00:09:11,139 --> 00:09:12,779
Is it really so?

190
00:09:16,379 --> 00:09:17,418
It's like this.

191
00:09:17,418 --> 00:09:17,979
No.

192
00:09:18,298 --> 00:09:19,379
Why not?

193
00:09:28,139 --> 00:09:28,739
Mr. Yu.

194
00:09:29,019 --> 00:09:30,019
Mr. Chu.

195
00:09:33,458 --> 00:09:36,178
I injured his meridians
in a moment's thought.

196
00:09:36,298 --> 00:09:37,619
His life is not in danger,

197
00:09:38,139 --> 00:09:39,218
but he

198
00:09:39,818 --> 00:09:41,899
might not be able
to practice martial arts anymore.

199
00:09:43,499 --> 00:09:44,779
I am busy with mundane affairs.

200
00:09:45,259 --> 00:09:47,098
I'll entrust him to you.

201
00:09:51,739 --> 00:09:52,739
Leader.

202
00:09:52,859 --> 00:09:54,139
Why?

203
00:09:54,379 --> 00:09:56,578
If you are to destroy him, why save him?

204
00:09:57,098 --> 00:09:58,899
If he survives,

205
00:09:59,058 --> 00:10:00,058
don't you

206
00:10:00,259 --> 00:10:02,019
fear that he will seek revenge on you?

207
00:10:05,458 --> 00:10:08,458
I made this choice
for the peace of the martial world.

208
00:10:08,818 --> 00:10:11,259
If I don't take action,
I can't convince the masses.

209
00:10:13,418 --> 00:10:16,139
Now, I feel guilty.

210
00:10:17,779 --> 00:10:18,979
Please help me save him.

211
00:10:19,818 --> 00:10:21,019
If he grows up

212
00:10:21,139 --> 00:10:23,259
and wants to seek revenge on me,

213
00:10:23,859 --> 00:10:24,938
by then,

214
00:10:26,298 --> 00:10:29,499
just tell him my name.

215
00:10:38,818 --> 00:10:41,298
Chu Wuya deceived all of us,

216
00:10:41,659 --> 00:10:43,418
saving that boy's life

217
00:10:44,458 --> 00:10:46,899
and giving him the chance
to seek revenge on us.

218
00:10:47,539 --> 00:10:50,472
It makes me to be
in such an awkward position now.

219
00:10:52,539 --> 00:10:53,539
Master.

220
00:10:53,818 --> 00:10:55,418
While I was tracking Chu Mengdie,

221
00:10:55,619 --> 00:10:56,979
I found Chu Wuya.

222
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:57,800
What?

223
00:10:59,218 --> 00:10:59,859
Where is he?

224
00:11:00,178 --> 00:11:01,578
The fishing village to the south.

225
00:11:02,139 --> 00:11:03,698
I had talked to him before.

226
00:11:03,859 --> 00:11:06,458
I found that he seems
to have forgotten who he is.

227
00:11:08,779 --> 00:11:09,938
You may leave.

228
00:11:11,458 --> 00:11:12,458
Yes.

229
00:11:20,139 --> 00:11:22,344
I'm blessed by heaven.

230
00:11:23,499 --> 00:11:26,280
I finally have my chance.

231
00:11:27,418 --> 00:11:28,424
This tea is excellent.

232
00:11:29,578 --> 00:11:30,938
I purchased it at a high price,

233
00:11:31,139 --> 00:11:32,259
with an excellent taste.

234
00:11:32,818 --> 00:11:33,818
Try it.

235
00:11:35,739 --> 00:11:37,619
You still have the mood
to drink tea now?

236
00:11:38,458 --> 00:11:40,019
If he and his daughter join forces,

237
00:11:40,139 --> 00:11:42,499
I'm afraid there will be no day
for us to turn the tables.

238
00:11:43,298 --> 00:11:44,338
Act

239
00:11:44,818 --> 00:11:45,859
in accordance

240
00:11:46,499 --> 00:11:47,144
with nature.

241
00:11:49,218 --> 00:11:51,368
The name of Wuwei Cave
is particularly well-chosen.

242
00:11:52,098 --> 00:11:52,744
Wuwei.

243
00:11:53,259 --> 00:11:56,298
It means act in accordance with nature.

244
00:11:56,418 --> 00:11:59,624
It seems that you have long
seen through the world.

245
00:12:00,698 --> 00:12:01,320
I admire you.

246
00:12:02,568 --> 00:12:04,008
What do you mean?

247
00:12:05,859 --> 00:12:07,659
If I were like you,

248
00:12:07,938 --> 00:12:10,539
facing a little setback
and ignoring everything,

249
00:12:11,058 --> 00:12:12,779
you and I would have been destituted.

250
00:12:15,899 --> 00:12:18,058
The sage always values difficulties,

251
00:12:18,379 --> 00:12:20,379
thus, there is no end to difficulty.

252
00:12:21,979 --> 00:12:24,298
Forgive my incompetence

253
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,499
for not helping you.

254
00:12:30,019 --> 00:12:30,696
You loser!

255
00:12:40,139 --> 00:12:41,218
I have thought it through.

256
00:12:41,938 --> 00:12:43,818
Instead of seeking physicians
for my father,

257
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:45,499
he might feel better

258
00:12:45,619 --> 00:12:46,899
if I let him stay here

259
00:12:47,098 --> 00:12:48,379
and live an ordinary life.

260
00:12:49,619 --> 00:12:51,298
I'm happy that you think like this.

261
00:12:53,298 --> 00:12:54,499
I really

262
00:12:54,938 --> 00:12:56,379
thank you.

263
00:12:57,178 --> 00:12:58,338
Instead of thanking me,

264
00:12:58,779 --> 00:12:59,458
you should...

265
00:12:59,739 --> 00:13:02,379
You should thank this naive kid.

266
00:13:02,379 --> 00:13:04,938
Chu Wuya is your father,

267
00:13:05,218 --> 00:13:07,859
and then becomes
the foster father of him.

268
00:13:08,818 --> 00:13:10,499
It seems you two are destined

269
00:13:11,938 --> 00:13:13,539
to meet.

270
00:13:15,659 --> 00:13:16,659
You old man!

271
00:13:16,779 --> 00:13:17,979
All you know is slacking off.

272
00:13:18,098 --> 00:13:19,818
Come play with me.

273
00:13:20,338 --> 00:13:20,904
Alright.

274
00:13:25,619 --> 00:13:26,739
Come on.

275
00:13:31,464 --> 00:13:32,200
Young lady.

276
00:13:33,139 --> 00:13:34,218
I got news from the manor.

277
00:13:34,659 --> 00:13:35,298
In half a day,

278
00:13:35,418 --> 00:13:37,218
four major sects
will arrive at Jingyun Manor.

279
00:13:38,058 --> 00:13:39,218
They intend to

280
00:13:39,218 --> 00:13:41,058
force us to organize troops to attack

281
00:13:41,298 --> 00:13:41,992
