00:30:24,539 --> 00:30:26,939
You didn't tell me that you're coming.

568
00:30:27,098 --> 00:30:28,138
I roasted something.

569
00:30:28,338 --> 00:30:29,338
Come join us.

570
00:30:32,578 --> 00:30:33,578
Nan Wentian!

571
00:30:35,779 --> 00:30:36,818
I respect you

572
00:30:37,578 --> 00:30:38,818
as you are a senior.

573
00:30:39,304 --> 00:30:40,658
Please do not do anything

574
00:30:40,658 --> 00:30:41,699
that will let me down.

575
00:30:43,019 --> 00:30:44,818
Who do you think you are?

576
00:30:45,378 --> 00:30:47,419
How dare you to tell me what to do?

577
00:30:48,019 --> 00:30:49,179
I expelled you,

578
00:30:49,298 --> 00:30:50,779
which is sparing your life.

579
00:30:51,419 --> 00:30:52,539
You're standing in my way.

580
00:30:53,298 --> 00:30:54,298
Get lost!

581
00:30:56,298 --> 00:30:57,298
Don't come closer.

582
00:31:01,858 --> 00:31:02,858
You ask for it.

583
00:31:13,338 --> 00:31:14,179
Let go.

584
00:31:14,338 --> 00:31:15,338
No way.

585
00:31:20,058 --> 00:31:20,618
Let go!

586
00:31:20,618 --> 00:31:21,618
No way.

587
00:31:21,898 --> 00:31:22,939
I promised Mengdie

588
00:31:23,378 --> 00:31:24,499
to protect her father.

589
00:31:25,298 --> 00:31:26,499
No way!

590
00:31:53,858 --> 00:31:54,378
Senior,

591
00:31:54,739 --> 00:31:55,858
stop!

592
00:31:57,699 --> 00:31:58,699
Senior.

593
00:32:00,259 --> 00:32:01,259
Senior.

594
00:32:02,219 --> 00:32:03,858
Mr. Chu has already gone mad.

595
00:32:04,378 --> 00:32:06,138
Just let him go.

596
00:32:10,019 --> 00:32:11,499
What are you saying?

597
00:32:12,378 --> 00:32:14,219
I had no intention of killing Mr. Chu.

598
00:32:14,818 --> 00:32:17,259
I just came to visit him.

599
00:32:17,739 --> 00:32:20,058
After all, the three of us

600
00:32:20,539 --> 00:32:22,138
haven't seen each other for so long.

601
00:32:22,939 --> 00:32:24,419
Right, Mr. Chu?

602
00:32:27,898 --> 00:32:30,338
You're all here? Stay for the meal.

603
00:32:32,419 --> 00:32:33,179
Hey!

604
00:32:33,419 --> 00:32:34,419
Time to eat.

605
00:33:18,658 --> 00:33:20,338
(There's a tradition in my hometown)

606
00:33:20,779 --> 00:33:21,818
that if a lady meets a man

607
00:33:22,098 --> 00:33:23,618
she fancies after coming of age,

608
00:33:24,259 --> 00:33:25,779
she makes him a dagger.

609
00:33:31,779 --> 00:33:32,779
(Baili Xingchen.)

610
00:33:34,378 --> 00:33:35,459
(This dagger)

611
00:33:36,818 --> 00:33:38,098
(is my gift to you.)

612
00:33:38,578 --> 00:33:39,578
Right.

613
00:33:39,739 --> 00:33:41,019
My harpoon is so noticeable.

614
00:33:41,138 --> 00:33:42,219
You'll be discovered.

615
00:33:42,939 --> 00:33:43,939
Take this one instead.

616
00:33:44,058 --> 00:33:44,739
Be careful

617
00:33:44,979 --> 00:33:45,979
and you won't be noticed.

618
00:34:38,716 --> 00:34:41,178
(Riyue Palace)

619
00:34:41,178 --> 00:34:42,178
Report!

620
00:34:45,419 --> 00:34:46,419
Leader.

621
00:34:46,499 --> 00:34:47,499
There is no one here.

622
00:34:47,658 --> 00:34:48,939
The living supplies are gone.

623
00:34:49,258 --> 00:34:50,738
They might know we would attack

624
00:34:50,899 --> 00:34:52,058
and have prepared to escape.

625
00:34:52,499 --> 00:34:53,499
They escaped?

626
00:34:54,339 --> 00:34:55,618
Such a large Riyue Palace,

627
00:34:55,778 --> 00:34:57,019
yet without a single person?

628
00:34:57,379 --> 00:34:59,578
Gu Yuan dared to snatch

629
00:34:59,698 --> 00:35:01,178
the manual at the Houlang Conference.

630
00:35:01,499 --> 00:35:02,698
He would never escape.

631
00:35:03,138 --> 00:35:04,138
Perhaps

632
00:35:04,459 --> 00:35:05,459
it's a trick.

633
00:35:06,058 --> 00:35:09,299
What can they accomplish?

634
00:35:09,618 --> 00:35:11,098
They are all cowards.

635
00:35:11,578 --> 00:35:13,098
No matter how brave they are,

636
00:35:13,299 --> 00:35:15,539
they wouldn't dare to oppose
the entire martial world.

637
00:35:16,778 --> 00:35:17,352
You

638
00:35:17,539 --> 00:35:19,138
take some people to investigate again.

639
00:35:19,499 --> 00:35:21,339
If we don't find Gu Yuan today,

640
00:35:22,819 --> 00:35:24,138
then go back and plan.

641
00:35:24,618 --> 00:35:25,218
Yes.

642
00:35:25,419 --> 00:35:26,578
You guys, come with me.

643
00:35:32,658 --> 00:35:34,178
Leader is indeed wise.

644
00:35:34,899 --> 00:35:36,419
Those followers of demon cult

645
00:35:36,618 --> 00:35:37,899
knew that today you

646
00:35:38,539 --> 00:35:40,459
intend to fight against Gu Yuan.

647
00:35:41,939 --> 00:35:42,939
I bet

648
00:35:43,778 --> 00:35:44,939
they were all scared away.

649
00:35:47,178 --> 00:35:47,819
Leader.

650
00:35:48,098 --> 00:35:51,258
I've already known where they are.

651
00:35:52,218 --> 00:35:53,618
We have too many people.

652
00:35:54,138 --> 00:35:55,499
I am afraid it will alert them.

653
00:35:55,859 --> 00:35:59,138
Maybe you and I go ahead first.

654
00:35:59,698 --> 00:36:01,019
You claim that.

655
00:36:01,738 --> 00:36:03,218
How do I know it's not a trap?

656
00:36:04,939 --> 00:36:06,299
Leader, don't worry.

657
00:36:06,899 --> 00:36:09,058
I will lead the way myself.

658
00:36:09,979 --> 00:36:12,258
Although I made a mistake,

659
00:36:12,738 --> 00:36:14,939
exterminating the demon cult

660
00:36:15,138 --> 00:36:16,138
is

661
00:36:16,539 --> 00:36:17,899
my responsibility.

662
00:36:20,218 --> 00:36:21,258
In that case,

663
00:36:21,658 --> 00:36:24,058
please lead the way, Master Nan.

664
00:36:24,339 --> 00:36:26,578
You and I will go together
to investigate.

665
00:36:28,819 --> 00:36:29,459
Young lady.

666
00:36:29,738 --> 00:36:31,178
I'm afraid he is deceiving us.

667
00:36:32,979 --> 00:36:34,339
He can't defeat me.

668
00:36:34,819 --> 00:36:36,539
Get ready
to provide support at any time.

669
00:37:22,299 --> 00:37:23,299
(Song'er.)

670
00:37:24,499 --> 00:37:27,138
(Back then, you didn't want me
to buy this fabric to make clothes.)

671
00:37:28,738 --> 00:37:30,258
(Did you already know)

672
00:37:31,859 --> 00:37:33,499
(I would wear this to take a risk?)

673
00:37:35,419 --> 00:37:36,618
(I'm sorry)

674
00:37:37,819 --> 00:37:39,339
(for letting you down.)

675
00:37:45,258 --> 00:37:46,899
(If we could have met earlier)

676
00:37:48,339 --> 00:37:49,672
(or I didn't know the ending,)

677
00:37:52,058 --> 00:37:53,256
(what would we be like?)

678
00:37:54,874 --> 00:37:57,064
♪Wherever the wind blows♪

679
00:37:57,258 --> 00:37:58,499
(It's a pity)

680
00:37:59,578 --> 00:38:01,019
(that I can't meet you)

681
00:38:02,979 --> 00:38:04,200
(in the Flower City.)

682
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:07,586
♪Be it clashing blades
or the mundane world♪

683
00:38:08,362 --> 00:38:10,770
♪The wind blows away the fog♪

684
00:38:10,770 --> 00:38:12,392
♪In a glance♪

685
00:38:25,208 --> 00:38:27,440
♪Wherever the wind blows♪

686
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:31,640
♪I share day and night with you♪

687
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:34,160
♪No matter what lies ahead♪

688
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:37,920
♪Be it clashing blades
or the mundane world♪

689
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:40,840
♪The wind blows away the fog♪

690
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:45,080
♪In a glance, I look into your eyes♪

691
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:51,440
♪Not regretting
my solitariness in this life♪

692
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:54,920
♪Never looking back
to find the way home♪

693
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:58,280
♪Why be confused about where to go♪

694
00:38:58,680 --> 00:39:04,320
♪A thousand threads of love
prevent me from stepping back♪

695
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:08,320
♪As winter passes,
frost flowers penetrate the bone♪

696
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:11,640
♪With spring's arrival,
longing colors the morning dew♪

697
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:17,760
♪Fortunate to express
infinite affection to someone♪

698
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:21,720
♪Better to draw a sword and dance
and write a book for you♪

699
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:24,680
♪We can run towards the future♪

700
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:28,400
♪Better not to speak of despair
but compose for love instead♪

701
00:39:28,824 --> 00:39:31,720
♪Do not fail the past♪

702
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:34,960
♪Better to be as initial as time fleets♪

